Package: sfextras
Type: Package
Title: Extra Functions for Simple Features
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Robin", "Lovelace", email = "rob00x@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5679-6536"))
      )
Date: 2021-01-07
Maintainer: Robin Lovelace <rob00x@gmail.com>
Description: Adds additional functionality to 'sf' objects in the 'sf' package
        <https://cran.r-project.org/package=sf>.
        The package provides functionality to run geographic
        functions on projected data, enabling operations such as
        buffers to work on data with geographic (longitude/latitude) coordinates.
